<P>
<P>
<UL>
<LI>There are no numbers in the WebTV Crossword. The clues for each word are
directly to the left of the puzzle. You will see the clues changing as you
navigate through the puzzle using the "up" and "down" arrows on your
keyboard or remote control.

<LI>To enter a word simply type the letters into the appropriate squares.

